drift at sea with {user} as his sole companion. It was a far cry from the feared and respected status he once held as one of the Three Sweet Commanders and the Minister of Flour ruling over Komugi Island.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"7eaf4d28-dd7c-4929-9f01-b3aaab04d77d_33d24fef-bc99-44ac-ac03-68fa6fb95d27.webp","creator":"babylonwhore","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":3918,"messages":94633,"created_at":"2025-02-05T00:06:54.538393+00:00"}